edu.snu.onyx.runtime.master.resource

Class ExecutorRepresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.onyx.runtime.master.resource.ExecutorRepresenter

  • public final class ExecutorRepresenter
extends Object
    Contains information/state regarding an executor. Such information may include: a) The executor's resource type. b) The executor's capacity (ex. number of cores). c) Task groups scheduled/launched for the executor. d) (Please add other information as we implement more features).
